st\n## Bag om kvanteteknologi / Quantum technology unpacked\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/697b5214986ac2465cde9919_AdobeStock_1570392172_.jpeg)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/67220ffe36d9614e9fc0dc64_Vectors-Wrapper.svg)\n### Fremtidens kapital\nPodcast\nJanuary 29, 2026\nHvad er kvanteteknologi? Og hvorfor dukker det op i debatter om innovation, national konkurrenceevne og langsigtede investeringer? I denne episode afmystificerer vi, hvad kvantefysik egentlig er, hvorfor den adskiller sig fundamentalt fra klassisk fysik, og hvordan de s\u00e6rlige principper bag kvanteteknologi nu baner vej for helt nye l\u00f8sninger.\nSammen med kvantefysikerne Kurt Stokbro og Helmut Katzgraber dykker vi ned i aktuelle og kommende anvendelser \u2013 fra kvantekommunikation og -sensorer til kvantecomputere. Vi ser n\u00e6rmere p\u00e5, hvilket potentiale teknologien rummer for virksomheder, produkter og vores samfund, og hvorfor det netop nu er strategisk vigtigt at forst\u00e5 og investere i kvanteomr\u00e5det.\nThomas Weisbjerg (Partner, Mazanti-Andersen) taler med Helmut Katzgraber (Chief Science Officer & Managing Partner, 55 North) og Kurt Stokbro (CEO, Sparrow Quantum).\n______\nWhat is quantum technology? And why is it showing up in conversations about innovation, national competitiveness, and long-term investments? In this episode, we demystify what quantum physics is, why it differs fundamentally from classical physics, and how the unique principles behind quantum technology are now paving the way for entirely new solutions.\nTogether with quantum physicists Kurt Stokbro and Helmut Katzgraber, we explore current and emerging applications, from quantum communication and sensors to quantum computers. We take a closer look at the potential this technology holds for businesses, products, and our society, and why it is strategically important to understand and invest in the quantum field right now.\nThomas Weisbjerg (Partner, Mazanti-Andersen) is joined by Kurt Stokbro (CEO, Sparrow Quantum) and Helmut Katzgraber (Chief Science Officer & Managing Partner, 55 North).\nListen to the episode [here](https://https-podcasts-apple-com-dk-podcast-bag-om-kvanteteknologi-quantum-technology-unpacked-id1854212773-i-1000747164948-l-da).\nPodcast\nJanuary 29, 2026\nInvestment from the Innovation Fund Denmark: 16.2 million kroner. \nDuration: 5 years. \nOfficial title: FTQP \u2013 \u2018Fault-Tolerant Architectures for Quantum Computing with Photon Emitters\u2019. \n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/67220ffe36d9614e9fc0dc64_Vectors-Wrapper.svg)\n### News\nStay updated with our latest news and insights. Check back regularly for updates on Sparrow Quantum and our industry.\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/67470d31233b5226ef909de1_Background-2-e1704370341365.png) Podcast January 3, 2024 Quantum Tech Pod, Ep.64: With Kurt Stokbro, CEO of Sparrow Quantum ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/quantum-tech-pod-ep-64-with-kurt-stokbro-ceo-of-sparrow-quantum)\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/6747274a343fd69f06893e9a_24486991-1.jpg) News January 19, 2023 Kvantestartup har udviklet en chip til fremti\u00addens supercom\u00adputer \u2013 jagter nu kapital ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/kvantestartup-har-udviklet-en-chip-til-fremtidens-supercomputer-jagter-nu-kapital)\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/6747161aa01726b5987c18a3_image%20672.jpeg) News June 25, 2024 Danske fotonkilder til fremtidens kvanteberegninger ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/danske-fotonkilder-til-fremtidens-kvanteberegninger)\n[![Sparrow Quantum logo with blue gradient color](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/6728a5364585a64f06e02a6e_Logo%20-%20Left%20Aligned.svg)](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/fremtidens-kapital)\nUnlocking Quantum Breakthroughs,   \nOne Photon at a Time\nAddress\n[Nordre Fasanvej 215  \n2000 Frederiksberg  \nDenmark  \nCVR. 36998717](https://maps.app.goo.gl/LhwCTfMwYQrr9w1R8)\nInfo\ninfo@sparrowquantum.com[+ 45 31 13 66 55](tel:+4531136655)[Privacy Policy](https://sparrowquantum.com/privacy-policy)\nSocials\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/sparrow-quantum/)[X](https://x.com/sparrow_quantum)[Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/@SparrowQuantum)\n\u00a92026 - Sparrow Quantum\n",
